Simple ODE framework based on odeint for iOS.

Requirements:

Mac OS X 10.7
Xcode 4.2
CMake 2.8

Compile:

Simple build:

cd path/to/iNumerics

./make.sh   (building for device)

or

./make.sh simulator  (building for simulator)


Manual build:

cd path/to/iNumerics
mkdir build && cd build

cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../toolchain/iOS.cmake -GXcode ..    (building for device)

or

cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../toolchain/iOS.cmake -DIOS_PLATFORM=SIMULATOR -GXcode ..    (building for simulator)

xcodebuild -target install -configuration Release


The static library can be found in path/to/iNumerics/dist
